title: China launches reusable rocket, second stage enters planned orbit, while first stage recovery test fails
description: China launched a reusable carrier rocket on Wednesday from northwest China. The second stage of this rocket managed to enter the designated orbit, but recovery of its first stage failed, according to the Xinhua News Agency.
